description:
Proper Japanese Title: 宇宙英雄物語 (Uchuu Eiyuu Monogatari)

Originally serialized in Monthly Comic Comp, when that magazine was cancelled in 1994, Future-Retro Hero Story was left without a home and left incomplete until it was picked up by Shueisha who finished serializing it in Ultra Jump and reprinted these first volumes (as well as collecting the new chapters).
name: Future-Retro Hero Story
